summary.span: 包含不用于从代码中直接使用的编译器生成的类型。

span.span: Contains compiler-generated types that are not intended to be used directly from your code.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 不使用或包含此命名空间。Do not use or include this namespace. 此命名空间的目的是为容器类是 XAML 标记编译器生成的 XAML 类型解析对程序集的内部帮助器。The purpose of this namespace is a container for the class is an internal helper that the XAML markup compiler produces for XAML type resolution against assemblies.
